snippet.textDisplay: @zak832 You're misinformed. They didn't throw Kirby in this game to make some extra cash. Good-Feel told Nintendo that they didn't like how their game turned out, and thought that it was missing something. Nintendo offered Good-Feel Kirby, they accepted, and think that it fixed the problems they had with the game.
